snippet.title: CarX Street PC - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
CarX Street PC - Official Gameplay Trailer.

CarX Street PC launches on August, 29.
Conquer mountain roads, highways, and city streets. Build your dream car with detailed tuning that unleashes the potential of “CarX Technology”© physics. Take part in thrilling races, enjoying realistic gameplay and dynamic driving.

Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1114150/CarX_Street
Social Media:

Twitter: https://twitter.com/carx_technology
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/carx_tech
Facebook (CarX Street): https://www.facebook.com/carxstreet
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/carx2/
CarX Store: https://carx-store.com
